{
  "_comment": "Firebase Realtime Database Security Rules — projet cmcteams-c16ab (Apex + CMCteams + Shops)",
  "_database": "cmcteams-c16ab-default-rtdb.europe-west1.firebasedatabase.app",
  "_phase": "4.2 (2026-07-04) : /apex + /coffre_vault exigent auth != null (comme /cmcteams depuis 2026-06-12). Prérequis livrés : repli anonyme Apex v13 (firebase-auth-bridge) + coffre-fort anon auth + push-worker/handoff/backup en service account. Le .write de /apex passe au niveau $key pour que les .write:false des clés secrètes (ax_pin, ax_user…) soient réellement effectifs (un .write parent ne peut pas être révoqué plus bas en RTDB). Regex $key élargie : apex_v13_* + vault_backup + users (chemins réellement écrits par l'app).",
  "_published_by": "Kevin DESARZENS",
  "_published_at": "2026-07-04",
  "_rollback": "deploy-cmcteams-rules.yml input apex_state=open (remet /apex + /coffre_vault en lecture/écriture libres) ; rules_state=open pour rouvrir /cmcteams. Le reste est inchangé.",
  "_instructions": [
    "1. Console Firebase > project cmcteams-c16ab > Realtime Database > Rules",
    "2. Copier-coller l'objet 'rules' ci-dessous",
    "3. Cliquer Publier",
    "",
    "PHASE 4 DURCIE = active actuellement",
    "  - Bloque l'écriture des secrets (PINs admin, clés API)",
    "  - Bloque la pollution avec clés arbitraires (validation $key regex)",
    "  - Garde lecture libre (compatibilité app sans Firebase Auth)",
    "",
    "PHASE 5 STRICTE = à publier APRÈS déploiement apex-auth-worker (cf. _phase5_after_worker)",
    "  - Exige auth.uid sur tous les paths per-user",
    "  - Émission de custom tokens par apex-auth-worker (services/apex-auth-worker/)",
    "  - Workflow auto-deploy : .github/workflows/deploy-apex-auth-worker.yml"
  ],
  "rules": {
    ".read": false,
    ".write": false,
    "cmcteams": {
      ".read": "auth != null",
      ".write": "auth != null",
      "$key": {
        ".validate": "$key.matches(/^(cmc_|ax_cmc_)[a-z0-9_\\-]+$/)"
      },
      "cmc_admin_pin": {
        ".write": false
      },
      "cmc_ia_key": {
        ".write": false
      },
      "cmc_motd": {
        ".validate": "newData.hasChildren(['text','ts','author']) || newData.val() === null"
      },
      "cmc_e": {
        ".validate": "newData.isString() == false"
      },
      "cmc_ov": {
        ".validate": "newData.isString() == false"
      },
      "cmc_pw": {
        ".validate": "newData.isString() == false",
        "$uid": {
          "clear": {
            ".validate": false
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "apex": {
      ".read": "auth != null",
      "$key": {
        ".write": "auth != null",
        ".validate": "$key.matches(/^(ax_[a-z0-9_\\-]+|apex_v13_[a-z0-9_\\-]+|vault_backup|users)$/)"
      },
      "ax_admin_pass": {
        ".write": false
      },
      "ax_admin_pin": {
        ".write": false
      },
      "ax_pin": {
        ".write": false
      },
      "ax_user": {
        ".write": false
      },
      "ax_uid": {
        ".write": false
      }
    },
    "coffre_vault": {
      ".read": "auth != null",
      ".write": "auth != null",
      "$uid": {
        ".validate": "$uid.matches(/^u_[a-z0-9]+$/)",
        "salt": {
          ".validate": "newData.isString() && newData.val().length < 64"
        },
        "verify": {
          ".validate": "newData.isString() && newData.val().length < 4096"
        },
        "meta": {
          ".validate": "newData.isString() && newData.val().length < 5242880"
        },
        "chunks": {
          "$id": {
            ".validate": "$id.matches(/^it_[a-z0-9_\\-]+$/) && (newData.val() === null || (newData.isString() && newData.val().length < 1048576))"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "shops_admin_v1": {
      "orders": {
        ".read": true,
        "$shop": {
          ".validate": "$shop.matches(/^(tech-hub|chez-lolo|ecocraft|digital-vault|pawsome|la-detente)$/)",
          "$orderId": {
            ".write": "!data.exists() && newData.hasChildren(['orderId','shop','total','ts'])",
            ".validate": "$orderId.length <= 40 && newData.child('total').isNumber() && newData.child('total').val() >= 0 && newData.child('total').val() < 100000 && newData.child('shop').isString() && newData.child('shop').val().length <= 40 && (!newData.hasChild('items_summary') || newData.child('items_summary').val().length <= 400)"
          }
        }
      },
      "products": {
        ".read": true,
        "$shop": {
          ".validate": "$shop.matches(/^(tech-hub|chez-lolo|ecocraft|digital-vault|pawsome|la-detente)$/)",
          "$id": {
            ".write": "newData.hasChildren(['id']) || !newData.exists()",
            ".validate": "$id.length <= 80 && (!newData.exists() || (newData.child('id').isString() && (!newData.hasChild('title') || newData.child('title').val().length <= 200) && (!newData.hasChild('image') || newData.child('image').val().length <= 600)))"
          }
        }
      },
      "logos": {
        ".read": true,
        "$shop": {
          ".validate": "$shop.matches(/^(tech-hub|chez-lolo|ecocraft|digital-vault|pawsome|la-detente)$/)",
          "$id": {
            ".write": true,
            ".validate": "$id.length <= 80 && (!newData.exists() || (!newData.hasChild('url') || newData.child('url').val().length <= 600))"
          }
        }
      },
      "access": {
        "_comment": "Fermé (audit 2026-07-07) : world-read fuitait les empreintes admin boutique + world-write = un inconnu s'ajoutait admin. Le client chez-lolo retombe sur l'admin maître codé en dur (Kevin/Laurence) + cache local, aucune casse. Multi-admin futur = passer par /__admin authentifié.",
        ".read": false,
        ".write": false
      },
      "ld_wiped_v1": {
        ".read": true,
        ".write": true,
        ".validate": "newData.isBoolean() || newData.val()===null"
      }
    },
    "shops_sourcing_v1": {
      "selection": {
        ".read": true,
        "$id": {
          ".write": "newData.hasChildren(['id','supplier']) || !newData.exists()",
          ".validate": "$id.length <= 120 && (!newData.exists() || (newData.child('supplier').val().length <= 60 && (!newData.hasChild('title') || newData.child('title').val().length <= 200) && (!newData.hasChild('image') || newData.child('image').val().length <= 600) && (!newData.hasChild('url') || newData.child('url').val().length <= 600)))"
        }
      }
    },
    "ld_detente": {
      ".read": true,
      "push_sub": {
        ".read": true,
        ".write": true,
        ".validate": "!newData.exists() || newData.isString()==false || newData.val().length<8000"
      }
    }
  },
  "_phase5_after_worker": {
    "_comment": "À publier quand apex-auth-worker est déployé ET que tous les clients Apex émettent des custom tokens. Garde les rules CMCteams et shops_admin_v1 actuelles, durcit uniquement /apex avec auth.uid per-user.",
    "rules_phase5_apex_only": {
      "apex": {
        "$key": {
          ".validate": "$key.matches(/^ax_[a-z0-9_\\-]+$/)"
        },
        "ax_admin_pass": {
          ".write": false,
          ".read": "auth != null && auth.token.role === 'admin'"
        },
        "ax_admin_pin": {
          ".write": false,
          ".read": false
        },
        "ax_pin": {
          ".write": false,
          ".read": false
        },
        "ax_user": {
          ".write": false,
          ".read": false
        },
        "ax_uid": {
          ".write": false,
          ".read": false
        },
        "ax_voice_print_$uid": {
          ".read": "auth != null && auth.uid === $uid",
          ".write": false
        },
        "ax_pin_$uid": {
          ".read": "auth != null && (auth.uid === $uid || auth.token.role === 'admin')",
          ".write": false
        },
        "ax_user_chat_$uid": {
          ".read": "auth != null && (auth.uid === $uid || auth.token.role === 'admin')",
          ".write": "auth != null && auth.uid === $uid"
        },
        "ax_user_locations_$uid": {
          ".read": "auth != null && auth.uid === $uid",
          ".write": "auth != null && auth.uid === $uid"
        },
        "ax_health_reports_$uid": {
          ".read": "auth != null && auth.uid === $uid",
          ".write": "auth != null && auth.uid === $uid"
        },
        "ax_msgs_$conv": {
          ".read": "auth != null",
          ".write": "auth != null"
        },
        "ax_settings_$uid": {
          ".read": "auth != null && (auth.uid === $uid || auth.token.role === 'admin')",
          ".write": "auth != null && auth.uid === $uid"
        },
        "ax_auth_log": {
          ".read": "auth != null && auth.token.role === 'admin'",
          ".write": "auth != null"
        },
        "ax_audit": {
          ".read": "auth != null && auth.token.role === 'admin'",
          ".write": "auth != null"
        },
        "ax_security_log": {
          ".read": "auth != null && auth.token.role === 'admin'",
          ".write": "auth != null"
        },
        "ax_breach_log": {
          ".read": "auth != null && auth.token.role === 'admin'",
          ".write": "auth != null"
        },
        "ax_telemetry_in": {
          ".read": "auth != null && auth.token.role === 'admin'",
          ".write": "auth != null"
        },
        "ax_claude_todo": {
          ".read": "auth != null && auth.token.role === 'admin'",
          ".write": "auth != null"
        },
        "ax_lessons_learned_struct": {
          ".read": "auth != null",
          ".write": "auth != null && auth.token.role === 'admin'"
        },
        "$other": {
          ".read": "auth != null",
          ".write": "auth != null && auth.token.role === 'admin'"
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "_phase_shops_rolelock": {
    "_comment": "Lockdown shops par RÔLE. Activé via deploy-cmcteams-rules.yml input shops_lock=on (ou SHOPS_LOCK=on). Le script applique ces .write aux écritures admin (products/logos/selection) → seuls Kevin/Lolo (id_token role:admin minté par kdmc-router /__admin/fbtoken derrière le GRANT admin) peuvent écrire. Les commandes clients (orders) et les LECTURES restent inchangées. À activer SEULEMENT après que le router est redéployé avec les secrets FB et qu une écriture admin a été testée (sinon écritures admin bloquées — pas les clients).",
    "writes": {
      "shops_admin_v1/products/$shop/$id": "auth != null && auth.token.role === 'admin' && (newData.hasChildren(['id']) || !newData.exists())",
      "shops_admin_v1/logos/$shop/$id": "auth != null && auth.token.role === 'admin'",
      "shops_sourcing_v1/selection/$id": "auth != null && auth.token.role === 'admin' && (newData.hasChildren(['id','supplier']) || !newData.exists())"
    }
  }
}
